VIOV: Vanguard S&P Small-Cap 600 Value Index Fund

The advisor employs an indexing investment approach designed to track the performance of the S&P SmallCap 600Â® Value Index, which represents the value companies, as determined by the index sponsor, of the S&P SmallCap 600 Index.
